imdb.plot outline: Spirit Seekers parodies the ever popular "Ghost Busters" culture. It crosses the lines by infusing real world elements with situational comedy. It's like a direct spinal tap designed to tickle your funny bone when it isn't scaring the daylights out of you. Ever brushed shoulders with the paranormal before? Now you can! Every haunted location is real, jam packed with legends, mysteries and urban myths. Even the psychics on this show are true practiced professionals. Together, this team of investigators brave everything from the surreal architecture of Winchester Mansion, to the legends of Oak and Roanoke Islands. They'll even endure three nights in the seedy dungeons of Alcatraz! Will they survive? Probably. After all, it's in the best interest of the spirits to postpone these idiots from ever gaining access to the afterlife.
imdb.title: Spirit Seekers
plot: _Spirit Seekers_ (qv) is a half hour series about a group of Adventurers in search of answers to one of life's greatest mysteries. The Afterlife.::Vito D'Amico & Geoff Hart
